
# Complete Frontend Folder Architecture (Reconciled)

This is the official frontend folder architecture after reconciliation.

It resolves the earlier conflict by clearly separating:
- module UI/domain implementation
- feature entitlement runtime
- view framework
- shell/layout
- services

---

# 1. Guiding Rule

Use this ownership split:

- `features/` = UI/domain implementation
- `feature-system/` = capability entitlement and runtime resolution
- `views/` = reusable view primitives and layouts
- `services/` = backend/Supabase access layer

`feature-system/` is the source of truth for runtime feature availability.

